    "next-main": {
      "type": "text",
      "variant": "prose",
      "props": {
        "content": "The next implementation slice should be **D0**: create `dna/core/tmux-harness.dna.yaml`, add report-only shape gates, and point `dna/core/harness` at the tmux-specific DNA instead of bloating the generic harness contract.\n\nAfter D0, do **D1** before source movement: generate the 29-row old-bridge behavior matrix and bind every behavior to a current owner-local test/eval or a rejection rationale. That prevents the refactor from quietly deleting behavior."
      }
    },
